00:48:38.630 --> 00:48:41.420 align:middle line:84%
And for all the dives I do
and all the visualization,

00:48:41.420 --> 00:48:44.910 align:middle line:84%
all the work I do, I always
connect it with breath work,

00:48:44.910 --> 00:48:49.820 align:middle line:84%
because then you have
doubled up on the efficiency.

00:48:49.820 --> 00:48:52.280 align:middle line:84%
When you link the breathing
to all the positive

00:48:52.280 --> 00:48:55.280 align:middle line:84%
reinforcement-- all the
happy thoughts, basically,

00:48:55.280 --> 00:48:57.260 align:middle line:90%
