sequence as you're actually

00:51:06.550 --> 00:51:09.530 align:middle line:90%
doing the sport.

00:51:09.530 --> 00:51:13.780 align:middle line:84%
To me, visualization is the
creative principle of life.

00:51:13.780 --> 00:51:15.330 align:middle line:84%
And I think we've
just all lost that.

00:51:15.330 --> 00:51:17.730 align:middle line:10%
I think in indigenous
cultures all around the world,

00:51:17.730 --> 00:51:19.590 align:middle line:10%
