00:51:19.590 --> 00:51:22.140 align:middle line:10%
And as a kid, we used dream.

00:51:22.140 --> 00:51:23.160 align:middle line:90%
We used imagination.

00:51:23.160 --> 00:51:25.050 align:middle line:90%
We used that creative faculty.

00:51:25.050 --> 00:51:27.790 align:middle line:84%
And I think it is the
creative faculty of life.

